					<br/><br/>Do you want to show this message in the future?","Keyboard Layout","No","Yes"] call BIS_fnc_guiMessage;

		waituntil {!isnil "_answer" && !dialog};

		profileNamespace setVariable ["MCC_FCtutorialPRKeys",!_answer];
	};
};